snippet.title: Make the Burger Trailer
snippet.description:
Make burgers with assorted ingredients, memorize orders and be quick before time runs out. Make your customers happy by eating delicious hamburgers, but remember, nobody likes to get wrong orders.
http://bit.ly/3bekXlA

Follow Creative Hand on Twitter: https://twitter.com/CreativeHandOf

About Creative Hand.
It is a developer of computer games, casual, quality and fun. 
We create our own games and we also support independent developers, focusing on the indie community.
